<span id="freeTextContainer1715509276692717549">This first book felt like 4 stars to me but the second book turns out to be a disappointment and I was able to give it 2,5 stars only. <br/><br/>This first book ends in a cliffhanger and their HEA comes at the end of second book but it could easily have been one book because the follow-up is certainly a dragging one.<br/><br/>My review for Book 1 &amp; 2 is here: <br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2550465725'>https://www.goodreads.com/review/show...</a><br/><br/>I will definitely not be reading Book 3, which as the writer says at the end of Book 2, is an extra -i.e. a bonus book</span>
  <span id="freeText1715509276692717549" style="display:none">This first book felt like 4 stars to me but the second book turns out to be a disappointment and I was able to give it 2,5 stars only. <br /><br />This first book ends in a cliffhanger and their HEA comes at the end of second book but it could easily have been one book because the follow-up is certainly a dragging one.<br /><br />My review for Book 1 &amp; 2 is here: <br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2550465725">https://www.goodreads.com/review/show...</a><br /><br />I will definitely not be reading Book 3, which as the writer says at the end of Book 2, is an extra -i.e. a bonus book for the lovers of this couple and I believe I have had enough already...<br /><br />*********************************************<br /><br />You can follow <a href="https://www.instagram.com/booksandmorebydvt/" rel="nofollow noopener">my instagram page from here</a></span>
