  <u>5 STARS!!!</u>
</b><br/><br/>First off, I have to say this was my first read from Ms. Georgia Cates and it did not disappoint one bit. I loved everything about this book from start to finish it was an overall fantastic read.<br/><br/><a href='http://s1343.beta.photobucket.com/user/ddes021/media/happydance_zps5b113022.gif.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
