  <b>Jack &amp; Laurelyn</b>
</u><br/>(The book didn’t mention him having any yummyyy scruffy facial hair however I picture my Aussie with lol) :)))<br/><br/><a href='http://s1343.beta.photobucket.com/user/ddes021/media/photo_zps8ec66d96.jpg.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
