</a><br/><br/><b>“They agreed on three months...but their love knew no boundaries.”</b><br/><br/><a href='http://s1343.beta.photobucket.com/user/ddes021/media/sweet_zpse674be6b.gif.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
